{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2376787, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "斯德哥尔摩？", "timestamp": 1630150908, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376789, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有的，我姐跟我爸也是这样，剧烈得争吵柔在很深刻的感情里就会是有点尴尬的", "timestamp": 1630150940, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376790, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "将来不给他养老就行了", "timestamp": 1630150949, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376793, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我没做过过分的事，我爸也这样骂我，经常喊我垃圾、傻逼，还说是为了我好才骂我，我不爱他", "timestamp": 1630150970, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376798, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": 2376790, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 什么意思？", "timestamp": 1630150974, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376799, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可以肯定的是你对你爸是有很深的感情的～", "timestamp": 1630150979, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376800, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我也，我从小就是姥姥带大的，带到了初中毕业", "timestamp": 1630150981, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376810, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不过我和我爸就关系一般，也像最熟悉的陌生人", "timestamp": 1630151038, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376812, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我的建议：分开一段时间，尝试找一下你跟你爸每次交流矛盾点在哪？", "timestamp": 1630151053, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376818, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "家庭还是应该通过感情来交流来解决问题～", "timestamp": 1630151102, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376820, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": 2376818, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 不认同", "timestamp": 1630151122, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376821, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": 2376818, "tag": null, "text": "有些人不配做父亲", "timestamp": 1630151133, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376832, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这些不用担心吧，说实话我们以后一年都不一定跟父母说几句话", "timestamp": 1630151199, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376833, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": 2376821, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 但是洞主很明显跟他爸是有感情的～，", "timestamp": 1630151203, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376838, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": 2376793, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 抱抱，其实dz自己也不觉得自己做过很过分的事，一直都是极乖极听话的，只是心里压抑过久有时会有言语上（或者神态表情上）的顶撞和发泄，就会被我爸骂", "timestamp": 1630151239, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376839, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我对家里人从来没有称呼，都是“欸”“嘿”地叫", "timestamp": 1630151252, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376844, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": 2376833, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 是的，我爸也很爱我，我有时觉得自己真不是人", "timestamp": 1630151283, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376849, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": 2376839, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 我也是，叫“诶”……", "timestamp": 1630151296, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376907, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": 2376832, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 一年都不说几句话如果没啥不可原谅的有些冷漠了吧", "timestamp": 1630151910, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376922, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": 2376839, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 嘿，您猜怎么着，诶，就是玩儿", "timestamp": 1630152091, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376940, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 453964, "reply_to": 2376907, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 没有任何矛盾，但不见面真的没什么话可说", "timestamp": 1630152231, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 453964, "reply": 21, "tag": null, "text": "虽然这个洞可能会被骂……\ndz从小和爸妈相处时间少，童年整三年是姥姥姥爷带的，和父母短暂地住在一起过，那段时间父亲也每晚忙工作，常常在我睡觉后才回家。我和父亲之间由于种种原因，时常产生矛盾，我做过很过分的事，他也和我说过很多遍“滚得越远越好”“你就是个畜牲”“你以后怎么样我看得透透的”这样的话（dz是女生）。\ndz和爸爸在一起相处，总觉得很尴尬，就是我很爱他，但是没办法敞开心扉，没办法表现得自然。我对姥姥姥爷每晚说“晚安”，对妈妈虽然不会那么亲，但也会叫“妈”，和她轻松愉快地相处。只是对父亲，我似乎很久没叫过“爸”了，就是觉得很尴尬很别扭。在和第三个人（其他亲人）说话的时候，说“我爸”怎样怎样倒是很自然。我知道这样很不好，也很想自然地一口一个“爸”，和他轻松地相处。但不知道为什么我真的很别扭，不知道dy有没有人能理解我？或者骂醒我也可以。", "timestamp": 1630150812, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1630152231, "url": "", "vote": {}}}